C%202026.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c5169d732a024514713598%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222797%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeta's%20president%2C%20Dina%20Powell%20McCormick%2C%20says%20the%20US%20will%20need%20a%20whole%20new%20workforce%2C%20including%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20electricians%2C%20to%20win%20the%20AI%20race.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Cooper%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeta's%20president%20said%20the%20US%20needs%20a%20%26quot%3Bwhole%20new%20workforce%26quot%3B%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20will%20need%20500%2C000%20electricians%20in%202%20years%20to%20build%20AI%20infrastructure%2C%20Dina%20Powell%20McCormick%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20the%20real%20heroes%20that%20are%20building%20the%20very%20infrastructure%20that%20will%20help%20us%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAmerica's%20effort%20to%20win%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-layoffs-ai-race-blueprint-reorg-bernstein-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20race%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20hinge%20on%20tradespeople.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20Meta's%20president%20and%20vice%20chairman%2C%20Dina%20Powell%20McCormick%2C%20who%20said%20the%20US%20will%20need%20a%20%26quot%3Bwhole%20new%20workforce%26quot%3B%20to%20stay%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetas-reality-labs-shifts-to-ai-native-pods-efficiency-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompetitive%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20talk%20about%20America%20and%20how%20critical%20it%20is%20that%20we're%20competitive%20in%20the%20AI%20race%2C%20we%20need%20a%20whole%20new%20workforce%2C%26quot%3B%20Powell%20McCormick%20said%20at%20the%20Axios%20AI%20Summit%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20much%20of%20the%20attention%20around%20AI%20has%20focused%20on%20chips%2C%20models%2C%20and%20engineers%2C%20she%20pointed%20to%20what%20she%20called%20%26quot%3Bthe%20workforce%20of%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20tradespeople%20responsible%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frolls-royce-caterpillar-cash-in-on-ai-boom-data-centers-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20the%20physical%20infrastructure%20behind%20the%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20in%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20500%2C000%20electricians%20are%20needed%20to%20build%20all%20the%20infrastructure%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20needed%20just%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20comments%20come%20as%20Meta%20and%20other%20tech%20giants%20are%20cutting%20roles%20and%20reshaping%20their%20workforces%20while%20pouring%20billions%20into%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-layoffs-job-cuts-ai-reality-labs-recruitment-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebegan%20laying%20off%20hundreds%20of%20employees%20this%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20divisions%20including%20Reality%20Labs%2C%20recruiting%2C%20sales%2C%20and%20global%20operations%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20and%20LinkedIn%20posts%20from%20affected%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20leaked%20internal%20memo%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%20shows%20the%20company%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetas-reality-labs-shifts-to-ai-native-pods-efficiency-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereorganizing%20parts%20of%20Reality%20Labs%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20small%2C%20%26quot%3BAI-native%26quot%3B%20pods%20of%20%26quot%3BAI%20builders%2C%26quot%3B%20part%20of%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20push%20to%20make%20Meta%20leaner%20and%20more%20productive%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cuts%20reflect%20a%20broader%20shift%20across%20Big%20Tech%2C%20where%20companies%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20do%20more%20with%20fewer%20people%2C%20especially%20in%20corporate%20and%20software%20roles%2C%20even%20as%20demand%20for%20skilled%20labor%20in%20construction%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20data%20center%20development%20surges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20we%20talk%20about%20it%20as%20the%20workforce%20of%20America%20because%20if%20you're%20competing%20on%20behalf%20of%20America%2C%20these%20are%20the%20real%20heroes%20that%20are%20building%20the%20very%20infrastructure%20that%20will%20help%20us%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20Powell%20McCormick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204326560-dac4-44b4-aa8e-c5ebb212a273%5C%22%3EThe%20AI%20boom%20is%20driving%20demand%20for%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20worker%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPowell%20McCormick%20isn't%20the%20only%20executive%20to%20have%20emphasized%20the%20need%20for%20tradespeople%2C%20as%20the%20AI%20infrastructure%20booms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20January%2C%20Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20said%20it%20was%20a%20good%20time%20to%20be%20a%20tradesperson%20because%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-plumber-construction-jobs-ai-data-center-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20boom%20is%20creating%20demand%20for%20manual%20labor%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20build%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20annual%20letter%20to%20shareholders%2C%20BlackRock%20CEO%20Larry%20Fink%20said%20the%20AI%20boom%20is%20already%20driving%20demand%20for%20skilled%20tradespeople%20building%20the%20infrastructure%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20live-streamed%20tech%20show%20TBPN%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20former%20Uber%20CEO%20Travis%20Kalanick%20said%20the%20AI%20boom%20could%20make%20plumbers%20far%20more%20valuable%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20most%20of%20the%20world%20were%20automated%2C%20physical%20work%20would%20become%20the%20%26quot%3Blong%20pole%20in%20th