20is%20actually%20smaller%20than%20both%20the%20Quarter%20Pounder%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%204%20ounces%20of%20pre-cooked%20beef%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20Big%20Arch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI'm%20typically%20not%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20the%20Big%20Mac.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcdonalds%20big%20mac%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c41c15732a024514713159%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20find%20the%20extra%20bun%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20burger%20to%20make%20the%20sandwich%20a%20little%20dry%2C%20even%20with%20the%20cheese%20and%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20underwhelmed%20by%20the%20Big%20Mac%20during%20this%20taste%20test%2C%20too.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcdonalds%20big%20mac%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c41abb299090a8c09b62f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20the%20Big%20Mac%20lacked%20flavor.%20I%20thought%20the%20lettuce%20was%20a%20little%20bland%2C%20the%20pickles%20weren't%20super%20sour%20or%20crunchy%2C%20and%20the%20burger%20needed%20more%20sauce%20to%20moisten%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20thought%20the%20burger%20was%20a%20little%20bottom-heavy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cheese%20and%20layers%20of%20Big%20Mac%20sauce%20were%20all%20layered%20toward%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20burger%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20top%2C%20which%20meant%20the%20dry%20bun%20and%20burger%20were%20hitting%20the%20roof%20of%20my%20mouth%20with%20little%20to%20no%20flavor%20or%20moisture%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Big%20Arch%20felt%20like%20McDonald's%20answer%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bpremium%26quot%3B%20burger.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcdonalds%20big%20arch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c41ac0732a02451471313d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20burger%20was%20previously%20tested%20in%20international%20markets%2C%20such%20as%20the%20UK%2C%20before%20it%20was%20added%20as%20a%20limited-time%20nationwide%20offering%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Big%20Arch%20came%20on%20a%20sesame%20seed-poppy%20seed%20bun.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcdonalds%20big%20arch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c41abb299090a8c09b62f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Big%20Arch%20comes%20topped%20with%20two%20quarter-pound%20patties%2C%20three%20slices%20of%20white%20cheddar%2C%20crispy%20and%20raw%20onions%2C%20lettuce%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20a%20new%2C%20tangy%20Big%20Arch%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20two%20thick%20patties%20and%20no%20middle%20bun%2C%20it%20was%20noticeably%20heavier%20than%20a%20Big%20Mac%20upon%20the%20first%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThis%20burger%20was%20tasty%20and%20beyond%20savory.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcdonalds%20big%20arch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c41abf48461c18d7be5fa7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20very%20filling%2C%20and%20I%20loved%20the%20addition%20of%20the%20white%20cheddar%20cheese%20%E2%80%94%20it%20tasted%20like%20a%20real%20steakhouse%20burger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C