20will%20be%20deciding%20between%20the%20Roam%202%20and%20the%20Play.%20Between%20these%20two%2C%20the%20Play's%20sound%20quality%20wins%20handily.%20Even%20at%2030%25%20volume%20level%2C%20the%20Play%20is%20room-filling.%20The%20Roam%202%20can%20hold%20its%20own%2C%20but%20it%20just%20doesn't%20have%20the%20same%20depth%20and%20range%20as%20the%20volume%20increases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20wanted%20a%20speaker%20to%20use%20exclusively%20for%20travel%2C%20I'd%20get%20the%20smaller%20Roam%202.%20Otherwise%2C%20I'd%20pick%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118305815faf-20%26h%3Dce2558200534b5d38887dba09f762157641e252bc4169d99d8a23ddffed4664f%26postID%3D69c3e29ad097316b35d9e378%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsonos-play-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSonos-Play-Portable-Bluetooth-Charging%252Fdp%252FB0GJRPCLGF%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESonos%20Play%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20everyday%20portable%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225483dece-b1c0-4d65-a145-3c7ff00143cd%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Sonos%20app%5C%22%3EThe%20Sonos%20app%20consideration%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20who%20have%20been%20in%20the%20Sonos%20ecosystem%20for%20a%20while%20might%20be%20worried%20about%20the%20company's%20mobile%20app%2C%20which%20was%20restructured%20from%20the%20ground%20up%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20and%20initially%20plagued%20by%20glitches.%20In%20short%2C%20I%20haven't%20had%20any%20problems%20with%20the%20app%20while%20testing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118305815faf-20%26h%3Dce2558200534b5d38887dba09f762157641e252bc4169d99d8a23ddffed4664f%26postID%3D69c3e29ad097316b35d9e378%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsonos-play-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSonos-Play-Portable-Bluetooth-Charging%252Fdp%252FB0G