A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpamela-anderson-dating-relationship-marriage-history-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eactor%20Pamela%20Anderson%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%20latest%20campaign%2C%20which%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eaims%20to%20drive%20home%20Aerie's%20%26quot%3B100%25%20Aerie%20Real%26quot%3B%20commitment.%20A%20video%20ad%20released%20Wednesday%20features%20Anderson%20attempting%20and%20failing%20to%20feed%20prompts%20to%20an%20AI%20generator%20to%20create%20realistic%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emodels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scene%20shifts%20to%20show%20Anderson%20sharing%20the%20set%20and%20laughing%20with%20three%20human%20models.%20The%20point%2C%20McCormick%20said%2C%20is%20to%20show%20that%20you%20can't%20prompt%20realness%20from%20AI%2C%20which%20is%20why%20Aerie%20uses%20humans%20without%20AI%20retouching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20the%20stance%20is%20important%20to%20build%20trust%20and%20credibility%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20our%20consumer%20that%20shops%20us%20and%20has%20been%20loyal%20to%20us%20knows%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20McCormick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Models%20posing%20for%20a%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c44d75299090a8c09b65b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221701%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20campaign%20video%20featured%20Anderson%20posing%20with%20three%20human%20models.%3Cp%3EAdrian%20Martin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Aerie%2C%20McCormick%20said%2C%20what%20you%20see%20is%20what%20you%20get%2C%20underscoring%20the%20brand's%20emphasis%20on%20transparency%20and%20authenticity.%20That's%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20it%20chose%20to%20partner%20with%20Anderson%2C%20who%20has%20made%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpamela-anderson-goes-makeup-free-at-fashion-week-photos-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emakeup-free%20look%20a%20part%20of%20her%20persona%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20red%20carpets%20and%20public%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2058-year-old%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpamela-anderson-career-change-oscar-buzz-the-last-showgirl-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaking%20a%20career%20comeback%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20her%20Netflix%20documentary%20%26quot%3BPamela%2C%20a%20Love%20Story%2C%26quot%3B%20acting%20roles%20in%20recent%20films%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BThe%20Last%20Showgirl%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20her%20presence%20at%20fashion%20week%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAerie%20hopes%20its%20target%20audience%20of%2024%20to%2035-year-olds%20%E2%80%94%20and%20younger%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20able%20to%20relate%20to%20Anderson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20it's%20important%20for%20the%20newer%20generation%2C%20who%20don't%20know%20us%2C%20to%20know%20that%20we%20won't%20generate%20bodies%2C%26quot%3B%20McCormick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e09bd102-4f31-42ac-8071-777cd00e8ef3%5C%22%3ERealness%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20brand%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAerie%20has%20made%20other%20commitments%20to%20transparency.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20would%20stop%20retouching%20people%20and%20bodies%20in%20its%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20October%2C%20it%20expanded%20on%20that%20by%20promising%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%20AI-generated%20bodies%20or%20people.%26quot%3B%20That%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faerie-against-ai-in-ads-most-liked-instagram-post-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eanti-AI%20pledge%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20the%20brand's%20most-liked%20Instagram%20post%20in%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20capped%20off%20a%20strong%20year%20for%20the%20lingerie%20brand.%20Parent%20company%20American%20Eagle%20Outfitters%20said%20Aerie's%20comparable%20sales%20increased%209%25%20in%20its%202025%20fiscal%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAerie%20isn't%20the%20only%20brand%20to%20push%20back%20against%20AI%20in%20advertising.%20Beauty%20brand%20Dove%20has%20pledged%20never%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20or%20distort%20women's%20bodies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcCormick%20said%20that%20while%20Aerie%20is%20completely%20opposed%20to%20using%20AI%20on%20people%20in%20its%20advertising%2C%20it's%20exploring%20ways%20to%20use%20the%20technology%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20supply%20chain%20management%2C%20content%20scaling%2C%20and%20planning.%20As%20the%20AI%20revolution%20continues%2C%20more%20companies%20are%20using%20it%20to%20automate%20processes%20and%20reduce%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20and%20those%20that%20don't%20could%20be%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20one%20place%20Aerie%20guarantees%20you%20won't%20see%20AI%3A%20on%20its%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20while%20AI%20can%20mimic%20an%20image%2C%20it%20can%20never%20capture%20the%20soul%2C%20warmth%2C%20or%20energy%20of%20a%20human%20being%2C%26quot%3B%20Jennifer%20Foyle%2C%20president%20and%20executive%20creative%20director%20for%20American%20Eagle%20and%20Aerie%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faerie-launches-anti-ai-campaign-featuring-pamela-anderson-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774530001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c42cfb48461c18d7be608f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faerie-launches-anti-ai-campaign-featuring-pamela-anderson-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pamela%20Anderson%20stars%20in%20Aerie's%20new%20anti-AI%20advertising%20campaign%2C%20highlighting%20the%20brand's%20commitment%20to%20using%20real%20people%20in%20its%20marketing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fae