ing%20a%20lot%20of%20multifamily%20and%20commercial%20properties%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20a%20couple%20of%20different%20cycles%20of%20the%20market%20%E2%80%94%20my%20parents%20were%20flipping%20houses%20back%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20so%20I've%20been%20following%20real%20estate%20since%20I%20was%20a%20teenager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20came%20in%20around%202018%2C%20it%20was%20a%20stable%20market%2C%20not%20too%20dissimilar%20to%20the%20market%20that%20we're%20in%20right%20now%2C%20but%20inventory%20would%20sit%20for%20a%20little%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20and%20now%2C%20we%20went%20through%20the%202.5%25%20interest%20rate%20market%2C%20which%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20fun.%20Back%20then%2C%20if%20you%20signed%20a%20listing%20agreement%2C%20you%20could%20already%20count%20the%20money.%20You%20could%20pretty%20much%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20getting%20that%20money%20in%20the%20next%2045%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20garage%20door%20opening%20into%20a%20coffee%20shop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2f7d4e98a37a4841f337a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESouthern%20Grounds'%20St.%20Petersburg%2C%20Florida%2C%20location.%3Cp%3ESouthern%20Grounds%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20it's%20like%20you%20can%20have%20eight%20listings%20worth%20of%20a%20total%20of%20%245%20million%20in%20volume%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20don't%20know%20how%20this%20is%20going%20to%20go.%20I%20think%20I'll%20get%20most%20of%20this%2C%20but%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomebuyers-remorse-cold-feet-purchase-cancellations-mortgage-rates-new-homes-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enot%20as%20much%20of%20a%20sure%20thing%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drastic%20change%20was%20very%20tough%20on%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20in%20my%20industry%20when%20it%20went%20from%20the%202022%20rates%20to%20the%202023%20rates%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b398fb9-ac8f-4ed0-94d8-17fe1901213e%5C%22%3EI%20used%20to%20work%20out%20of%20this%20coffee%20shop%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20invest%20in%20it%20myself%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20market%20was%20going%20well%2C%20previously%20I'd%20diversify%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-bought-airbnb-made-60000-three-years-2015-07%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuying%20Airbnbs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20a%20part%20in%20four%20Airbnbs%20at%20one%20time%20or%20another.%20Sometimes%20you%20sell%20them%20because%20it's%20just%20a%20good%20time%2C%20but%20that%20business%2C%20it's%20like%20you%20put%20up%20%2470%2C000%20in%20your%20savings%2C%20and%20you're%20happy%20to%20be%20getting%20a%20return%20of%20maybe%20%24800%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20now%20and%20then%2C%20there's%20a%20problem%20where%20you%20have%20to%20come%20up%20with%20%242%2C000%20to%20%245%2C000%20out%20of%20pocket.%20I%20thought%20this%20was%20a%20pretty%20good%20idea%20for%20investment%20if%20you're%2055%20years%20old%20%E2%80%94%20just%20keep%20stacking%20these%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20right%2C%20well%20that%20one%20will%20pay%20for%20my%20health%20insurance%2C%20and%20that%20one%20will%20pay%20for%20my%20car%20insurance%2C%20and%20that's%20great.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20was%20like%2C%20I'm%2030%20years%20old%2C%20why%20don't%20I%20take%20a%20stab%20at%20investing%20in%20something%20that%20could%20make%20me%20the%20same%20amount%20as%20real%20estate%20does%3F%20And%20once%20it's%20stabilized%2C%20it%20will%20not%20take%20up%20all%20my%20time%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20invest%20%2470%2C000%20and%20make%20%24800%20a%20month%2C%20but%20what%20if%20I%20could%20invest%20double%20that%20and%20potentially%20make%20%2412%2C000%20or%20%2413%2C000%20a%20month%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20good%20time%20in%20life%20for%20me%20to%20take%20that%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20colorful%20mural%20inside%20a%20coffee%20shop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2f7d4e98a37a4841f337b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHooten%20was%20able%20to%20make%20the%20investment%20due%20to%20his%20success%20as%20an%20agent.%3Cp%3ESouthern%20Grounds%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20doing%20so%20well%20in%20real%20estate%20that%20I%20was%20confident%20enough%20to%20invest%20over%20six%20figures%20in%20a%20coffee%20business.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20just%20coffee%3B%20it%20was%20specifically%20Southern%20Grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20didn't%20have%20an%20office%2C%20I%20used%20to%20go%20up%20to%20Southern%20Grounds%20in%20Jacksonville%20all%20the%20time.%20It%20was%20a%20place%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-baristas-feel-when-remote-workers-camp-coffee-shop-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20could%20sit%20on%20my%20laptop%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20order%20coffee%2C%20and%20didn't%20feel%20pressured%20to%20order%20food%20until%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20order%20food.%20If%20I%20wanted%20to%20stay%20and%20work%20on%20my%20laptop%20and%20make%20phone%20calls%20for%20four%20hours%2C%20I%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20founder%20on%20Facebook%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMan%2C%20I%20want%20to%20franchise%20your%20store.%20It's%20my%20favorite%20place%20in%20the%20world%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that's%20how%20all%20this%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20this%20process%20in%202022.%20We've%20been%20working%20on%20building%20this%20store%20for%20three%20and%20a%20half%20years%20from%20when%20we%20signed%20the%20Franchise%20Disclosure%20Document%20to%20when%20we%20actually%20opened%20our%20store%20in%20August%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20way%20we%20could%20have%20afforded%20to%20buy%20our%20building%20%E2%80%94%20it%20actually%20wouldn't%20even%20pencil%20if%20you%20look%20at%20it%20as%20a%20real%20estate%20deal.%20Our%20rent%20of%20%2413%2C500%20is%20probably%20half%20of%20what%20the%20mortgage%20would%20be%20if%20we%20bought%20it.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-business-moved-wall-street-st-petersburg-florida-not-miami-2026-03%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDowntown%20St.%20Petersburg%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20very%20overpriced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228660%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Downtown%20St.%20Petersburg%2C%20Florida.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c419da48461c18d7be5f9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225773%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESt.%20Petersburg%2C%20Florida.%3Cp%3ERudyBalasko%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20build%20the%20entire%20restaurant%20from%20looking%20like%20a%20garage%20into%20a%20restaurant.%20The%20construction%20alone%20was%20about%20%24800%2C000.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat's%20just%20to%20build%20out%20the%20interior%20of%20the%20building%20that%20we%20are%20renting%20%E2%80%94%20I%20mean%2C%20silverware%20for%20a%20restaurant%20is%20%2425%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20industry%2C%20your%20first%20year%20is%20not%20usually%20a%20good%20indicator%20of%20how%20you're%20going%20to%20do%20financially%2C%20just%20like%20the%20restaurant%20business.%20During%20my%20first%20year%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20I%20didn't%20do%20that%20well.%20So%20I%20would%20say%20I'm%20happier%20with%20the%20year%20one%20restaurant%20success%20than%20year%20one%20real%20estate%20success%2C%20for%20sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298d640d6-b779-454c-8466-4b08bd5518e7%5C%22%3EI'm%20glad%20I%20took%20a%20risk%20and%20diversified%20my%20income%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bartended%20in%20college%2C%20so%20I've%20always%20been%20on%20the%20hospitality%20side%20of%20business%2C%20and%20I%20guess%20you%20could%20say%20real%20estate%20is%20hospitality%3A%20It's%20being%20a%20people%20person%2C%20enjoying%20talking%20to%20people%2C%20enjoying%20hearing%20their%20stories%20and%20where%20different%20people%20are%20from%20and%20what%20they're%20doing%20and%20what%20they've%20got%20going%20on%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20weekend%20%E2%80%94%20just%20caring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20transaction%20volume%20is%20still%20the%20same%20since%20before%20I%20bought%20the%20coffee%20shop.%20My%20real%20estate%20business%20has%20taken%20a%20slight%20hit%20because%20it%20hasn't%20continued%20to%20grow%20in%20the%20way%20that%20I%20think%20it%20may%20have%20grown%20had%20I%20not%20taken%20on%20any%20other%20endeavors.%20But%20ultimately%2C%20I'm%20not%20losing%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20the%20coffee%20shop%20really%20has%20not%20changed%20my%20day-to-day%3B%20it%20has%20just%20required%20more%20time%20management%20and%20multitasking.%20I%20wake%20up%20earlier%20and%20work%20later.%20I'm%20working%20my%20ass%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20for%20real%20estate%20agents%20to%20diversify%20their%20income.%20It%20really%20just%20depends%20on%20each%20person's%20financial%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I%20wonder%2C%20%26quot%3BDid%20I%20make%20the%20right%20decision%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20I%20did%20because%20I%20enjoy%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agent-side-hustle-franchised-coffee-shop-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774525081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4196948461c18d7be5f96%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agent-side-hustle-franchised-coffee-shop-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jordan%20Wooten%20is%20a%20real%20estate%20agent%2