20tanks%20ahead%20of%20an%20announced%20gas%20price%20hike.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cars%20line%20up%20for%20gas%20in%20China.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4119f48461c18d7be5f2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMotorists%20queue%20to%20fill%20their%20tanks%20ahead%20of%20a%20petrol%20price%20adjustment%20expected%20on%20March%2023%2C%20at%20a%20petrol%20station%20in%20Suzhou%2C%20in%20China's%20eastern%20Jiangsu%20province%20on%20March%2022%2C%202026.%3Cp%3ECN-STR%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20National%20Development%20and%20Reform%20Commission%20had%20initially%20announced%20that%20the%20set%20average%20price%20of%20gas%20would%20rise%20from%20%244.20%20a%20gallon%20to%20%245.10%20a%20gallon%2C%20an%20increase%20of%2090%20cents%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2026%2F03%2F23%2Fbusiness%2Fchina-gasoline-prices.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20On%20Monday%2C%20the%20agency%20said%20the%20planned%20increase%20would%20be%20lowered%20to%2050%20cents%2C%20bringing%20the%20price%20to%20%244.70%20a%20gallon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECustomers%20in%20Santiago%2C%20Chile%2C%20also%20rushed%20to%20gas%20stations%20on%20Tuesday%20ahead%20of%20a%2054%25%20increase%20in%20fuel%20prices.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cars%20line%20up%20for%20gas%20in%20Chile.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4127a48461c18d7be5f3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECustomers%20wait%20in%20line%20to%20fuel%20up%20vehicles%20at%20a%20gas%20station%20in%20Santiago%2C%20Chile%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20March%2024%2C%202026.%20Chile's%20government%20will%20hike%20fuel%20prices%20by%20as%20much%20as%2054%25%20on%20Thursday%2C%20stoking%20expectations%20for%20a%20steep%20rebound%20in%20inflation%20and%20triggering%20a%20wave%20of%20panic%20buying%20at%20gasoline%20stations%20across%20the%20country.%3Cp%3ECristobal%20Olivares%2FBloomberg%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJorge%20Quiroz%2C%20Chile's%20finance%20minister%2C%20announced%20that%20the%20price%20hikes%20would%20take%20effect%20on%20Thursday%2C%20sparking%20panic%20buying%20as%20vehicle%20owners%20sought%20to%20fill%20their%20tanks%20before%20the%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20Bangkok%2C%20gas%20stations%20faced%20fuel%20shortages.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Empty%20signs%20on%20gas%20pumps%20in%20Thailand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c41006732a0245147130d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBANGKOK%2C%20THAILAND%20-%202026%2F03%2F16%3A%20Several%20gas%20stations%20across%20Bangkok%20have%20reported%20temporary%20fuel%20shortages%2C%20with%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20stock%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bawaiting%20delivery%26quot%3B%20signs%20posted%20at%20pumps.%20The%20crisis%20stems%20from%20escalating%20military%20tensions%20between%20the%20U.S.%2C%20Israel%2C%20and%20Iran%2C%20which%20have%20severely%20disrupted%20global%20energy%20supplies%20and%20caused%20the%20national%20Oil%20Fund%20to%20plummet.%20This%20geopolitical%20instability%20has%20sparked%20widespread%20panic%20buying%20and%20fuel%20hoarding%20among%20the%20public%2C%20leading%20to%20localized%20shortages.%20Consequently%2C%20rising%20transportation%20costs%20are%20now%20trickling%20down%20to%20consumer%20goods%2C%20driving%20up%20prices%20and%20causing%20nationwide%20economic%20distress.%3Cp%3EArnun%20Chonmahatrakool%2FThai%20New%2FThai%20News%20Pix%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20pumps%20featured%20signs%20reading%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20stock%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bawaiting%20delivery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20some%20parts%20of%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20gas%20prices%20exceeded%20%248%20per%20gallon.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gas%20over%20%248%20per%20gallon%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c41295732a0245147130ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELos%20Angeles%2C%20CA%20-%20March%2019%3A%20A%20gas%20station%20on%20Thursday%2C%20March%2019%2C%202026%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20CA%3Cp%3EEric%20Thayer%2FLos%20Angeles%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20March%2025%2C%20the%20average%20price%20per%20gallon%20of%20regular%20gasoline%20in%20California%20was%20%245.831%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgasprices.aaa.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAAA%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20national%20average%20across%20the%20US%20was%20%243.983%20per%20gallon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGas%20prices%20in%20California%20are%20typically%20higher%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20due%20to%20state%20taxes%2C%20stricter%20environmental%20regulations%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bcleaner%26quot%3B%20gas%20blends%2C%20and%20limited%20supply%20compared%20to%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPorter%20Airlines%20announced%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20would%20institute%20a%20temporary%20fuel%20surcharge%20on%20some%20flights.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Porter%20Airlines%20planes%20at%20an%20airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4125248461c18d7be5f3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22579%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETORONTO%2C%20ON-%20MARCH%2023%20-%20Porter%20Airlines%20announced%20that%20due%20to%20the%20recent%20rise%20in%20global%20fuel%20prices%2C%20they%20are%20introducing%20a%20temporary%20fuel%20surcharge%20on%20all%20VIPorter%20flight%20redemptions.%20in%20Toronto.%20March%2023%2C%202026.%20This%20adjustment%20will%20be%20applied%20as%20a%20'Peak%20Surcharge'%20to%20each%20passenger%2C%20each%20way.%20This%20update%20goes%20into%20effect%20for%20all%20new%20VIPorter%20flight%20bookings%20as%20of%20March%2023%2C%202026%20-%20any%20existing%20bookings%20are%20unaffected.%20Steve%20Russell%2FToronto%20Star%3Cp%3ESteve%20Russell%2FToronto%20Star%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20flights%20booked%20with%20loyalty%20points%20through%20the%20Canadian%20airline's%20VIPorter%20redemption%20program%2C%20Porter%20began%20charging%20a%20%2440%20peak%20surcharge%20for%20flights%20within%20North%20America%20and%20an%20%2486%20fee%20per%20leg%20for%20international%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20be%20transparent%20about%20why%20this%20change%20is%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20Porter%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20customers.%20%26quot%3BFuel%20represents%20the%20highest%20cost%20of%20airline%20operations%20and%20this%20surcharge%20allows%20us%20to%20maintain%20the%20number%20of%20points%20required%20for%20redemption.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPresident%20Ferdinand%20Marcos%20of%20the%20Philippines%20declared%20a%20state%20of%20%26quot%3Bnational%20energy%20emergency%26quot%3B%20on%20Tuesday.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Philippine%20President%20Ferdinand%20Bongbong%20Marcos%20Jr.%20greets%20passengers%20on%20a%20bus.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4122d299090a8c09b628d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPhilippine%20President%20Ferdinand%20Bongbong%20Marcos%2C%20Jr%20(C)%20visits%20the%20Paranaque%20Integrated%20Terminal%20Exchange%20(PITX)%20to%20personally%20oversee%20the%20initial%20rollout%20of%20fuel%20subsidies%20for%20public%20utility%20vehicles%20(PUVs)%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20distribution%20process%20is%20smooth%20and%20well-organized%20in%20Metro%20Manila%2C%20Philippines%20on%20March%2024%2C%202026.%20With%20rising%20fuel%20prices%2C%20the%20government%20continues%20to%20provide%20financial%20assistance%20to%20drivers%20and%20operators%20of%20PUVs.%20The%20initiative%20is%20part%20of%20the%20PhP2.5-billion%20allocation%20for%20PUVs%20under%20the%20Department%20of%20Transportation%20(DOTr)%20Fuel%20Subsidy%20Project.%20Under%20the%20program%2C%20bus%20operators%20receive%20PhP10%2C000%20per%20unit%2C%20while%20drivers%20are%20entitled%20to%20PhP5%2C000%20each.%3Cp%3EPhilippine%20Presidential%20Com.%20Office%2FHandout%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20executive%20order%20stated%20that%20the%20war%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20had%20resulted%20in%20%26quot%3Bimminent%20danger%20posed%20upon%20the%20availability%20and%20stability%20of%20the%20country's%20energy%20supply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Philippines%20also%20rolled%20out%20fuel%20subsidies%20for%20public%20utility%20vehicles%20to%20help%20them%20absorb%20climbing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EStreet%20vendors%20in%20New%20Delhi%20have%20switched%20to%20electric%2C%20coal%2C%20wood%2C%20and%20kerosene%20stoves%20amid%20a%20shortage%20of%20LPG%20gas%20cylinders.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tea%20seller%20uses%20a%20coal%20stove%20in%20New%20Delhi.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4102d48461c18d7be5f1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22804%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENEW%20DELHI%2C%20INDIA%20-%20MARCH%2022%3A%20A%20tea%20seller%20use%20coal%20stove%20due%20to%20shortage%20of%20LPG%20Gas%20cylinder%20at%20Tank%20Road%20Karol%20Bagh%2C%20on%20March%2022%2C%202026%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20India.%20The%20crisis%2C%20triggered%20by%20the%20ongoing%20West%20Asia%20conflict%20and%20the%20blockade%20of%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20has%20forced%20thousands%20of%20Delhi's%20street%20vendors%20and%20dhaba%20owners%20to%20abandon%20gas%20burners%20for%20Electirc%20coal%2C%20wood%2C%20or%20kerosene%20stoves.%3Cp%3EIshant%20Chauhan%2FHindustan%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20shortage%20of%20liquefied%20petroleum%20gas%2C%20which%20is%20used%20across%20India%20for%20everyday%20cooking%2C%20a%20tea%20seller%20on%20Tank%20Road%20in%20Karol%20Bagh%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20was%20photographed%20heating%20up%20tea%20using%20a%20coal%20stove%20on%20Sunday.%20Many%20eateries%20in%20the%20country%20have%20had%20to%20scale%20back%20their%20menus%20or%20close%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESome%20fishing%20vessels%20in%20Thailand%20have%20halted%20operations%20due%20to%20the%20prohibitively%20high%20cost%20of%20boat%20fuel.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Docked%20fishing%20boats%20in%20Narathiwat%20Province%2C%20Thailand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c42154299090a8c09b6360%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDocked%20fishing%20boats%20in%20Narathiwat%20Province%2C%20Thailand.%3Cp%3EPloy%20Phutpheng%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2040%25%20of%20Thailand's%209%2C000%20registered%20fishing%20vessels%20have%20paused%20operations%2C%20a%20Thai%20official%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bangkokpost.com%2Fthailand%2Fgeneral%2F3221285%2Frising-fuel-costs-force-fishing-fleets-to-dock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBangkok%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reduction%20in%20fishing%20is%20expected%20to%20push%20up%20seafood%20costs.%20Seafood%20vendors%20have%20already%20raised%20prices%20of%20some%20items%20by%205%20to%2020%20baht%2C%20or%20between%20around%2015%20and%2061%20cents%2C%20per%20kilogram%2C%20according%20to%20The%20National%20Fisheries%20Association%20of%20Thailand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20closure%20of%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20has%20also%20raised%20concerns%20about%20global%20fertilizer%20supply%20shortages%20affecting%20food%20security%20and%20prices.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Kashmiri%20farmer%20sprinkles%20fertilizer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4116a299090a8c09b628a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAaqib%20Ahmad%2C%2023%2C%20a%20Kashmiri%20farmer%2C%20sprinkles%20fertilizer%20near%20a%20mustard%20field%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Srinagar%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20on%20March%2022%2C%202026.%20The%20ongoing%20Iran-Israel%20conflict%20has%20disrupted%20Middle%20East%20fertilizer%20supplies%2C%20with%20up%20to%2030%25%20of%20global%20urea%20shipments%20at%20risk%20due%20to%20closures%20and%20military%20operations%20around%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz.%20This%20situation%20is%20increasing%20global%20prices%2C%20affecting%20crop%20yields%20in%20the%20Northern%20Hemisphere%2C%20and%20adding%20pressure%20on%20global%20food%20security.%3Cp%3EFirdous%20Nazir%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20one-third%20of%20the%20global%20seaborne%20fertilizer%20trade%20passes%20through%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20released%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Functad.org%2Fnews%2Fhormuz-shipping-disruptions-raise-risks-energy-fertilizers-and-vulnerable-economies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUN%20Conference%20on%20Trade%20and%20Development%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20March%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20the%20shipping%20disruption%20is%20%26quot%3Braising%20concerns%20about%20ripple%20effects%20across%20global%20markets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-gas-prices-energy-crisis-photos-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774523521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c412d3299090a8c09b6298%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-gas-prices-energy-crisis-photos-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Energy%20costs%20are%20rising%20globally%20due%20to%20the%20closure%20of%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20during%20the%20Iran%20war.%20Other%20supply%20chains%20could%20also%20be%20in%20peril.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tlakritz%40businessinsider.com%20(Talia%20Lakritz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-gas-prices-energy-crisis-photos-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ravi%20Mohan%E2%80%99s%20Goa%20investments%20with%20Kenishaa%20sparks%20buzz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774523413000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129822674%2Cimgsize-119010.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fravi-mohans-goa-investments-with-kenishaa-sparks-buzz-parasakthi-actors-marital-status-claim-raises-big-questions%2Farticleshow%2F129822674.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129822674.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActor%20Ravi%20Mohan's%20recent%20property%20investment%20in%20Goa%20with%20Kenishaa%20Francis%20has%20ignited%20considerable%20discussion.%20The%20controversy%20stems%20from%20property%20documents%20reportedly%20listing%20Ravi%20Mohan%20as%20'unmarried%2C'%20despite%20his%20ongoing%20divorce%20proceedings%20with%20Aarti%20Ravi.%20This%20discrepancy%20has%20fueled%20speculation%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20deal%20and%20Kenishaa's%20invol