lt%3D%5C%22Enclave%20cofounders%20from%20left%20to%20right%3A%20CTO%20Dvir%20Segev%2C%20CEO%20Tal%20Hoffman%2C%20CPO%20Yanir%20Tsarimi%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4295248461c18d7be605c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221049%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEnclave%20cofounders%20from%20left%20to%20right%3A%20CTO%20Dvir%20Segev%2C%20CEO%20Tal%20Hoffman%2C%20CPO%20Yanir%20Tsarimi%3Cp%3EEnclave%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEnclave%20is%20launching%20from%20stealth%20with%20%246%20million%20in%20seed%20funding%20at%20a%20%2433%20million%20valuation%20led%20by%208VC.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20include%20Stripe%20cofounder%20Patrick%20Collison%2C%20Salesforce%20CEO%20Marc%20Benioff%2C%20and%20Yelp%20CEO%20Jeremy%20Stoppelman.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEnclave%20is%20focused%20on%20finding%20the%20most%20dangerous%20security%20flaws%20buried%20in%20the%20lines%20of%20code%20written%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEnclave%2C%20a%20startup%20focused%20on%20finding%20the%20most%20dangerous%20security%20flaws%20buried%20deep%20within%20code%20written%20by%20AI%2C%20is%20launching%20from%20stealth%20with%20%246%20million%20in%20seed%20funding%20at%20a%20%2433%20million%20valuation%2C%20led%20by%208VC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20round%20includes%20a%20roster%20of%20prominent%20tech%20investors%20and%20executives%2C%20including%20Stripe%20cofounder%20Patrick%20Collison%2C%20Salesforce%20CEO%20Marc%20Benioff%2C%20Box%20CEO%20Aaron%20Levie%2C%20and%20Yelp%20CEO%20Jeremy%20Stoppelman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E8VC's%20bet%20on%20Enclave%20is%20shaped%20in%20part%20by%20its%20investment%20in%20AI%20coding%20startup%20Cognition%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20the%20coding%20agent%20Devin%2C%20which%20gave%20it%20a%20front-row%20seat%20to%20how%20quickly%20AI-generated%20software%20is%20spreading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%20of%20that%2C%20we've%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20AI%20code%20generation%20both%20in%20our%20companies%20and%20in%20large%20enterprises%2C%26quot%3B%208VC's%20Vivek%20Gopalan%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BThe%20last-gen%20tools%20are%20not%20going%20to%20cut%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnclave%20was%20founded%20by%20CEO%20Tal%20Hoffman%2C%20CTO%20Dvir%20Segev%2C%20and%20CPO%20Yanir%20Tsarimi%2C%20who%20previously%20worked%20together%20in%20application%20security.%20Hoffman%20and%20Tsarimi%20met%20while%20serving%20in%20Israel's%20elite%20Unit%208200%2C%20a%20military%20intelligence%20unit%20widely%20known%20as%20a%20training%20ground%20for%20cybersecurity%20and%20AI%20talent.%20The%20unit%20has%20produced%20a%20number%20of%20prominent%20tech%20companies%2C%20including%20cybersecurity%20firms%20like%20Check%20Point%2C%20Palo%20Alto%20Networks%2C%20CyberArk%2C%20and%20Wiz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261a601c0-8808-4546-ba5d-23194c40ea91%5C%22%3EAI%20has%20proven%20very%20adept%20at%20coding%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%20said%20last%20year%20that%20up%20to%2030%25%20of%20the%20company's%20code%20is%20written%20by%20AI.%20Boris%20Cherny%2C%20founder%20and%20head%20of%20Claude%20Code%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fbcherny%2Fstatus%2F2015979257038831967%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20pretty%20much%20100%25%20of%20our%20code%20is%20written%20by%20Claude%20Code%20%2B%20Opus%204.5%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20had%20not%20written%20a%20single%20line%20of%20code%20in%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoffman%2C%20who%20started%20coding%20at%2012%2C%20estimates%20that%20up%20to%2060%25%20of%20code%20across%20all%20startups%20is%20written%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20a%20three-year%20time%20horizon%2C%20we're%20definitely%20going%20to%20cross%20it%2090%25%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20AI%20has%20made%20coding%20much%20faster%20at%20Enclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%20we%20were%20writing%20this%20massive%20feature%20that%20would%20normally%20take%20two%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAI%20did%20it%20in%20two%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20all%20the%20code%20generated%20by%20AI%20creates%20vulnerabilities%2C%20according%20to%20Hoffman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCurrent%20solutions%20are%20optimizing%20for%20quantity%2C%20not%20for%20quality%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnclave%20is%20entering%20a%20crowded%20application%20security%20market%20that%20includes%20companies%20like%20Snyk%2C%20Checkmarx%2C%20and%20Semgrep.%20Hoffman%20aims%20to%20stand%20out%20by%20focusing%20less%20on%20scanning%20for%20known%20issues%20and%20more%20on%20understanding%20systems%20holistically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20building%20that%20deep%20knowledge%20into%20how%20your%20systems%20behave%2C%20it's%20much%20easier%20to%20know%20where%20to%20look%20for%20vulnerabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-just-raised-6-million-from-8vc-and-marc-benioff-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774522801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c42aa648461c18d7be606d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-just-raised-6-million-from-8vc-and-marc-benioff-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Enclave%2C%20a%20startup%20focused%20on%20finding%20the%20most%20dangerous%20security%20flaws%20buried%20in%20the%20lines%20of%20code%20written%20by%20AI%2C%20is%20launching%20from%20stealth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bbergman%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Bergman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-just-raised-6-million-from-8vc-and-marc-benioff-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thyssenkrupp%2C%20Jindal%20Steel%20sale%20talks%20falter%20on%20pension%