ciding%20factor.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20like%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennials%20can't%20catch%20a%20break%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20looking%20to%20buy%20their%20first%20house%2C%20the%20market%20has%20been%20tough%20for%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-frozen-rate-lock-mortgage-rates-real-estate-market-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eessentially%20gridlocked%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20high%20prices%2C%20high%20mortgage%20rates%2C%20and%20low%20inventory.%20The%20job%20market%20is%20also%20in%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flow-hire-low-fire-layoffs-employees-stuck-unemployment-job-seekers-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreat%20Freeze%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%3A%20the%20unemployed%20can't%20find%20jobs%2C%20and%20those%20with%20them%20can't%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20has%20been%20one%20economic%20bright%20spot%20recently%20for%20the%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennial%20cohorts%3A%20how%20much%20money%20they've%20been%20pumping%20into%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20data%20from%20Bank%20of%20America%20shows%20that%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-losses-wealth-effect-iran-consumer-spending-q1-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espending%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%202025%20surpassed%20older%20generations%20like%20baby%20boomers%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20years.%20The%20reason%20why%20is%20encouraging%3A%20rent%20growth%20is%20cooling%20at%20a%20time%20when%20wage%20growth%20is%20heating%20up.%20Good%20vibes%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20I%20hate%20to%20be%20the%20bearer%20of%20bad%20news%2C%20but%20the%20Iran%20war%20could%20put%20an%20end%20to%20this%20still-nascent%20period%20of%20economic%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20most%20bearish%20scenarios%20involving%20the%20war%2C%20the%20flashpoint%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-straight-of-hormuz-crisis-stocks-bonds-treasurys-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoil-market%20disruption%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-map-us-states-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egas%20prices%20at%20the%20pump%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20pushing%20%244%20a%20gallon%20nationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20is%20the%20most%20exposed%2C%20BofA%20finds.%20It's%20the%20only%20generation%20to%20not%20see%20gasoline%20spending%20as%20a%20share%20of%20overall%20consumption%20fall%20from%20pre-pandemic%20levels.%20Millennials%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20seen%20a%20smaller%20decline%20than%20Gen%20X%20or%20boomers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBofA%20notes%20that%20Gen%20Z%20is%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20it's%20commuting%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%20income%20is%20still%20relatively%20low.%20Millennials%20may%20make%20more%20money%2C%20but%20they're%20raising%20families%20and%20doing%20the%20most%20driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20it%20in%20fully%20zoomed-out%20terms%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Ethe%20Iran%20war%20is%20threatening%20to%20cut%20off%20a%20spending%20resurgence%20for%20younger%20generations.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20variable%20going%20forward%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecession-outlook-mark-zandi-economy-oil-prices-job-market-iran-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elabor%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20BofA%20describes%20as%20being%20in%20a%20stable%20%26quot%3Blow-hire%2C%20low-fire%26quot%3B%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20is%20eyeing%20any%20prolonged%20impact%20from%20the%20Iran%20war%20on%20sectors%20like%20retail%20and%20leisure%2C%20which%20tend%20to%20employ%20more%20younger%20people.%20The%20industry%20has%20already%20taken%20a%20hit%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%20Further%20disru