Fabercrombie-former-ceo-jeffries-controversary-prior-to-arrest-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMichael%20Jeffries%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2081%2C%20was%20heard%20talking%20about%20possible%20defenses%2C%20including%20that%20his%20accusers%20were%20%26quot%3Badults%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20time%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20was%20no%20force%20involved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeffries%20also%20repeatedly%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20being%20found%20incompetent%20to%20stand%20trial%2C%20telling%20his%20co-defendant%2C%20longtime%20romantic%20partner%20Matthew%20Smith%2C%20in%20an%20August%202025%20prison%20tape%20that%2C%20otherwise%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20screwed%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20in%20big%20trouble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recordings%2C%20from%20Jefferies'%20four-month%20stay%20last%20year%20in%20the%20mental%20health%20unit%20of%20a%20North%20Carolina%20prison%2C%20were%20introduced%20on%20the%20second%20day%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabercrombie-and-fitch-ceo-michael-jefferies-competency-hearing-sex-trafficking-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethree-day%20competency%20hearing%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20federal%20court%20in%20Central%20Islip%2C%20NY.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeffries%2C%20who%20led%20Abercrombie%20%26amp%3B%20Fitch%20from%201992%20to%202014%2C%20is%20seeking%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabercrombie-fitch-ceo-prison-call-doctors-better-find-me-incompetent-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efound%20unfit%20for%20his%20October%20trial.%3C%2Fa%3E%20His%20lawyers%20argue%20he%20suffers%20from%20Alzheimer's%20disease%20and%20Lewy%20body%20dementia%20and%20cannot%20understand%20the%20charges%20or%20assist%20in%20his%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20steps%20into%20a%20car%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c3144458b5806618e7e0b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%