223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20men%20without%20shirts%20pose%20with%20a%20woman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c458b248461c18d7be62c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222120%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAbercrombie%20%26amp%3B%20Fitch%20Models%20at%20the%205th%20Avenue%20store%20opening%20in%20New%20York%20City%20in%202005%3Cp%3ECarley%20Margolis%2FFilmMagic%20for%20Paul%20Wilmot%20Communications%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20rode%20down%20Fifth%20Avenue%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeffries%20told%20a%20defense%20psychiatrist.%20%26quot%3BThey%20moved%20the%20fucking%20store%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20new%20location%20three%20blocks%20south%2C%20Jeffries%20said%20in%20the%20January%202026%20tape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20to%20cry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20psychiatrist%20Dr.%20Alexander%20Bardey%2C%20who%20testified%20Wednesday%20as%20a%20defense%20witness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20still%20crying%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeffries%20continued%20in%20the%20tape%2C%20his%20voice%20breaking%20with%20emotion%20as%20he%20remembered%20the%20flagship%20outlet%2C%20which%20he%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20beautiful%20store%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmy%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20doesn't%20make%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeffries%20said%20in%20the%20tape%2C%20telling%20the%20defense%20psychiatrist%2C%20%26quot%3Bbuild%20a%20story%20around%20%3Cem%3Ethat%3C%2Fem%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20prison%20tape%20captured%20a%20tender%20moment%20between%20Jeffries%20and%20Smith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20won't%20stand%20trial%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20is%20heard%20consoling%20Jeffries%20in%20the%20August%20recording.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20but%20%3Cem%3Eyou%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeffries%20responds%2C%20concern%20for%20his%20romantic%20partner%20apparent%20in%20his%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26q