E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang's%20direct%20reports%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20one-on-one%20meetings%20with%20the%20big%20boss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20spoke%20to%20podcaster%20Lex%20Fridman%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dvif8NQcjVf0%26t%3D409s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20episode%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20Monday%20about%20the%20way%20he%20leads%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20chipmakers%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20technological%20innovation.%20He%20said%20he%20runs%20his%20business%20differently%20from%20the%20way%20other%20trillion-dollar%20companies%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20said%20he%20oversees%20more%20than%2060%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-routine-management-leadership-style-ceo-founder-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epeople%20in%20his%20direct%20staff%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20he%20doesn't%20conduct%20one-on-one%20meetings%20with%20each%20of%20them.%20He%20said%20he%20prefers%20to%20tackle%20issues%20as%20a%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20one-on-ones%20with%20them%20because%20it's%20impossible%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20present%20a%20problem%2C%20and%20all%20of%20us%20attack%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20Nvidia's%20workflow%20as%20%26quot%3Bextreme%20co-design.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20he%20manages%20mostly%20engineers%20with%20expertise%20in%20areas%20like%20CPUs%2C%20GPUs%2C%20algorithms%2C%20and%20design.%20Huang%20addresses%20them%20together%2C%20and%20each%20person%20is%20expected%20to%20know%20when%20to%20chime%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhoever%20wants%20to%20tune%20out%2C%20tune%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20who%20are%20on%20the%20staff%2C%20they%20know%20when%20to%20pay%20attention.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Huang%20said%20he's%20not%20afraid%20to%20call%20out%20an%20employee%20for%20not%20contributing%20in