tine.%20Here's%20my%20advice%20for%20handling%20the%20TSA%20chaos.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman's%20head%20shot%2C%20long%20line%20at%20O'Hare%20Airport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c477e7299090a8c09b666f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeather%20Wagenknecht%20has%20changed%20her%20routine%20due%20to%20long%20airport%20lines%20(shown%20at%20O'Hare%20International%20Airport%20on%20March%2016).%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20photo%3B%20Getty%20image%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHeather%20Wagenknecht%20takes%20~150%20flights%20a%20year%20and%20spends%20as%20little%20time%20as%20possible%20in%20airports.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETSA%20and%20air%20traffic%20control%20staffing%20shortages%20have%20disrupted%20her%20travel%20routine%20and%20added%20stress.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe's%20now%20driving%20to%20destinations%20she%20would've%20flown%20to%20in%20the%20past%20and%20losing%20time%20with%20her%20kids.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Heather%20Wagenknecht%2C%20a%20vice%20president%20of%20sales%20for%20a%20company%20that%20deploys%20towers%20for%20public%20safety%20and%20telecom%20from%20Batavia%2C%20Illinois.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20VP%20of%20sales%20for%20my%20company%2C%20I%20average%20between%20100%20and%20150%20flights%20a%20year%2C%20and%20I%20have%2013%20flights%20just%20this%20month%20alone.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spend%20so%20much%20time%20in%20airports%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20there%20a%20minute%20longer%20than%20I%20have%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20typical%20airport%20schedule%20is%20to%20arrive%2015%20to%2020%20minutes%20before%20my%20flight%20boards%20and%20park%20in%20the%20garage.%20I%20head%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftried-clear-tsa-precheck-and-global-entry-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECLEAR%20plus%20PreCheck%20line%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20walk%20through%2C%20fill%20up%20my%20water%20bottle%2C%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom%2C%20and%20get%20on%20the%20plane.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20my%20routine.%20I%20have%20United%20Club%20access%20in%20case%20something%20doesn't%20go%20as%20planned%2C%20but%20my%20goal%20is%20never%20to%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20say%2090%25%20of%20the%20time%20this%20works%20for%20me.%20Have%20I%20missed%20a%20flight%3F%20Sure%2C%20but%20it's%20few%20and%20far%20between.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229982ab3-2cd4-4a79-b143-5cf0d6ef35de%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELonger%20lines%20and%20short-staffed%20air%20traffic%20control%20has%20impacted%20my%20recent%20trips%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20beginning%20of%20March%2C%20that's%20when%20I%20started%20seeing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-big-airports-tsa-worker-shortage-long-waits-government-shutdown-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eslower%20TSA%20lines%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20it%20wasn't%20even%20slower%20lines%2C%20they%20just%20didn't%20have%20as%20many%20lines%20open%2C%20which%20then%20caused%20a%20backlog%20%E2%80%94%20even%20to%20the%20PreCheck%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20longer%20lines%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-traffic-controllers-worlds-hardest-jobs-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eair%20traffic%20control%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ATC)%20has%20also%20been%20impacted.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20home%20last%20week%20from%20San%20Diego%2C%20my%20flight%20was%20delayed.%20We%20were%20in%20the%20air%2C%20and%20we%20got%20rerouted%20for%20over%20an%20hour%20because%20they%20said%20ATC%20was%20short-staffed%2C%20so%20they%20had%20to%20slow%20down%20planes%20coming%20into%20O'Hare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a497e60a-4549-47e0-94d3-57e5e1836b68%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20I've%20opted%20to%20drive%20when%20I%20usually%20would've%20flown%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20my%20daughter%20to%20her%20admitted%20students%20day%20in%20Kentucky%20this%20week%2C%20and%20had%20this%20stuff%20not%20been%20going%20on%2C%20we%20would've%20just%20flown%20to%20Lexington.%20It's%20rare%20you're%20going%20to%20get%20me%20in%20a%20car%20for%20six%20hours%20if%20I%20could%20fly.%20It's%20just%20easier%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20I%20fly%20to%20Detroit%2C%20Indianapolis%2C%20and%20Des%20Moines%20from%20my%20home%20airport%20of%20Chicago%20O'Hare.%20And%20right%20now%20I'd%20drive%20to%20any%20of%20those%20instead%20of%20flying%2C%20just%20to%20avoid%20the%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afc3fa44-5590-4a01-a202-f508c4f098f5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20arriving%20at%20the%20airport%20earlier%20than%20I%20usually%20would%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20main%20travel%20concern%20this%20week%20is%20the%20additional%20wait%20time%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20because%20the%20lines%20are%20throwing%20a%20kink%20in%20my%20routine.%20I%20know%20that%20sounds%20so%20selfish%2C%20because%20obviously%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-workers-could-miss-another-paycheck-partial-government-shutdown-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20aren't%20getting%20paid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20combat%20the%20long%20lines%2C%20I'm%20now%20trying%20to%20get%20there%20an%20hour%20before%20boarding%20begins%2C%20and%20I'm%20doing%20it%20begrudgingly.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20is%20going%20to%20Mexico%20on%20Saturday%2C%20and%20with%20checking%20bags%20we'll%20probably%20leave%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20earlier%20than%20normal%2C%20and%20we%20all%20have%20CLEAR%20plus%20PreCheck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ec99079-57b1-422b-aa64-b8527d961c8d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20travel%20chaos%20is%20impacting%20my%20work%20and%20home%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20is%20making%20my%20job%20more%20stressful.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20meeting%20in%20San%20Francisco%20this%20week%2C%20one%20of%20my%20colleagues%20was%20coming%20from%20Atlanta%2C%20and%20he%20got%20to%20the%20airport%20like%20two%20hours%20beforehand%20and%20decided%20he%20was%20leaving.%20He%20said%20Atlanta%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmass-tsa-delays-absences-flying-unpredictable-long-lines-wait-times-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emess%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20we%20decided%20to%20cancel%20the%20meeting%20and%20make%20it%20virtual%2C%20which%20was%20fine%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20inconvenient%20for%20the%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20personal%20life%2C%20it%20means%20earlier%20mornings.%20I%20try%20to%20spend%20as%20much%20time%20at%20home%20as%20I%20can%2C%20since%20I'm%20gone%20so%20much.%20Leaving%20for%20the%20airport%20three%20hours%20instead%20of%20an%20hour%20early%20means%20that's%20less%20I'm%20doing%20to%20help%20get%20kids%20out%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fda49a40-14af-464d-9979-71bcfe6a357d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20tips%20for%20travelers%20during%20these%20difficult%20times%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20advice%20I%20have%20is%2C%20if%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-precheck-etiquette-get-through-airport-security-fast%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecan%20get%20PreCheck%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20do%20it.%20If%20you%20can%20get%20touchless%20ID%2C%20do%20it.%20And%20if%20you%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20CLEAR%2C%20I'd%20say%20do%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20of%20those%20lines%20for%20the%20past%20six%20weeks%20have%20been%20better%20than%20the%20non-PreCheck%20lines.%20For%20our%20Mexico%20trip%2C%20we're%20going%20with%20three%20other%20families%20and%20I%20told%20them%3A%20You%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20everybody%20in%20your%20family%20has%20PreCheck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20bottom%20line%20message%20is%20patience.%20Stay%20flexible%2C%20and%20if%20you%20can%2C%20just%20get%20there%20early.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20just%20know%20that%20it%20sucks.%20It%20sucks%20for%20everybody.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20frequent%20business%20traveler%20with%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20how%20you're%20handling%20the%20current%20travel%20situation%3F%20Contact%20this%20editor%2C%20Debbie%20Strong%2C%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Adstrong%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edstrong%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-tsa-lines-ohare-airport-changed-my-work-travel-routine-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774517581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c477e7299090a8c09b666f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-tsa-lines-ohare-airport-changed-my-work-travel-routine-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Frequent%20business%20traveler%20Heather%20Wagenknecht%20likes%20to%20send%20as%20little%20time%20as%20possible%20at%20the%20airport.%20Recent%20TSA%20issues%20have%20disrupted%20her%20routine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kate%20Loweth)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-tsa-lines-ohare-airport-changed-my-work-travel-routine-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Super%20Micro%20shareholders%20sue%20company's%20CEO%20and%20CFO%20along%20with%20co-founders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774517504000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129820290%2Cimgsize-13088.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fsuper-micro-sued-by-shareholders-sue-compan