20threatening%20far%20more%20targets%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20in%20camouflage%20gear%20in%20a%20snowy%20brown%20field%20under%20a%20blue%20sky%20with%20one%20holding%20a%20large%20grey%20drone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c43f2b299090a8c09b6523%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20drones%20have%20created%20a%20host%20of%20new%20attacks%20for%20Ukraine%20to%20stop%2C%20just%20as%20Ukrainian%20ones%20have%20for%20Russia.%3Cp%3ERussian%20Defense%20Ministry%20%2F%20Handout%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESalvos%20can%20include%20dozens%20of%20drones%20at%20once.%20Even%20outside%20war%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrones-disrupting-denmark-airports-near-f-35-stealth-fighter-base-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrones%20have%20disrupted%20airports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cities%2C%20and%20military%20bases%20across%20the%20US%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDouglas%20Barrie%2C%20an%20air%20power%20expert%20at%20IISS%2C%20said%20air%20defense%20has%20gotten%20%26quot%3Bmore%20difficult%26quot%3B%20as%20ballistic%20missiles%20have%20proliferated%2C%20combat%20aircraft%20remain%2C%20and%20now%20there%20are%20huge%20masses%20of%20drones%20to%20stop%2C%20too.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20wicked%20problem%20set%20that's%20coming%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20shows%20what%20this%20looks%20like%20in%20practice.%20It%20fields%20a%20mix%20of%20Soviet-era%20systems%2C%20Western-donated%20defenses%2C%20and%20domestic%20solutions%20to%20protect%20both%20cities%20and%20military%20targets%2C%20yet%20%26quot%3Bthey%20still%20get%20hit%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Bronk%20said.%20Ukraine%20has%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-says-can-supply-interceptors-allies-stop-drone-attacks-investment-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echoices%20on%20its%20defense%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20it%20faces%20ballistic%20and%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20drones%2C%20and%20glide%20bombs%2C%20among%20other%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b379a90d-930d-451a-80d9-6e6f50f446e6%5C%22%3ETough%20decisions%20to%20make%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20Ukraine%20had%20twice%20as%20many%20US-made%20advanced%20Patriot%20air%20defense%20systems%2C%20Ryan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20would%20still%20need%20to%20make%20really%20hard%20choices%20about%20what%20the%20priorities%20to%20protect%20were.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20wider%20war%2C%20those%20tradeoffs%20could%20scale%20across%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20experience%2C%20Barrie%20said%2C%20shows%20that%20in%20such%20a%20conflict%20%26quot%3BEurope%20will%20inevitably%20have%20to%20make%20difficult%20choices.%26quot%3B%20Countries%20will%20need%20to%20identify%20what%20must%20be%20shielded%2C%20what%20they'd%20like%20to%20protect%2C%20and%20things%20that%20are%20simply%20going%20to%20be%20left%20undefended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224510%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Damaged%20buildings%20and%20a%20street%20full%20of%20rubble%20under%20a%20blue%20sky%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c43eaa299090a8c09b651d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223007%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20stop%20all%20of%20Russia's%20drone%20and%20missile%20attacks.%3Cp%3EViktoriia%20Yakymenko%2FSuspilne%20Ukraine%2FJSC%20%26quot%3BUA%3APBC%26quot%3B%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Western%20air%20force%20intelligence%20officer%20who%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20to%20discuss%20warfighting%20lessons%20said%20Ukraine%20is%20being%20forced%20into%20constant%20tradeoffs%20and%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20big%20one%20being%3A%20do%20you%20move%20air%20defenses%20forward%20to%20protect%20troops%20or%20hold%20them%20back%20to%20defend%20cities%3F%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EDuring%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20Western%20defenses%20prioritized%20nuclear%20forces%20to%20preserve%20deterrence%20%E2%80%94%20not%20cities%2C%20which%20were%20understood%20to%20be%20largely%20indefensible%20in%20full-scale%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20throw%20enough%20at%20air%20defense%20to%20defend%20everything%20from%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Bronk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219f8bf0b-d2e9-4793-88b8-689003d81a14%5C%22%3EAir%20defense%20is%20still%20essential%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20air%20defense%20capacity%20in%20the%20West%20is%20still%20deeply%20insufficient%20for%20a%20large-scale%20war%20or%20a%20protracted%20campaign.%20NATO%20lacks%20the%20necessary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-promise-air-defense-spending-money-alone-wont-solve-issue-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eground-based%20air%20defenses%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20rushing%20to%20buy%20more%2C%20but%20systems%20take%20years%20to%20produce%2C%20face%20backlogs%2C%20and%20are%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-interceptor-drones-air-defense-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECheap%20drone%20interceptors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20Ukraine%20is%20fielding%20at%20scale%2C%20are%20emerging%20but%20haven't%20yet%20spread%20widely%20across%20the%20alliance.%20Allies%20are%20now%20scrambling%20to%20buy%20them%2C%20with%20limited%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20a%20black%20outfit%20kneels%20on%20the%20grass%2C%20holding%20on%20to%20one%20of%20a%20host%20of%20small%20black%20interceptor%20drones%20that%20are%20on%20the%20ground%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c43e45732a02451471336