-corporate-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebankruptcy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20revealing%20in%20court%20papers%20that%20it%20owes%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20to%20music%20icon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbob-dylan-wife-kids-family-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBob%20Dylan%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECallaway%20Arts%20%26amp%3B%20Entertainment%2C%20Inc.%20filed%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fwhat-is-chapter-11-bankruptcy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChapter%2011%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fa%3E%20protection%20%E2%80%94%20a%20process%20that%20allows%20a%20company%20to%20restructure%20its%20debts%20under%20court%20supervision%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Manhattan%20federal%20bankruptcy%20court%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECourt%20filings%20by%20Callaway%20show%20that%20the%20company%20owes%20its%2020%20largest%20unsecured%20creditors%20more%20than%20%244%20million%2C%20including%20%24450%2C000%20to%20Dylan%20and%20nearly%20%241.7%20million%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fim-a-ceo-who-hosts-ama-sessions-with-employees-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHachette%20Book%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20publishers%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Callaway%20and%20its%20bankruptcy%20attorney%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20Representatives%20for%20Dylan%20and%20Hachette%20Book%20Group%20also%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECallaway's%20Chapter%2011%20petition%20does%20not%20specify%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20debts.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20company%20published%20the%20608-page%20book%20%26quot%3BBob%20Dylan%3A%20Mixing%20Up%20the%20Medicine%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20working%20life%20of%20the%20now-84-year-old%20Grammy-winning%20singer-songwriter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20year%2C%20Callaway%20and%20Hachette%20Book%20Group%20announced%20a%20partnership%20for%20the%20sales%20and%20distribution%20of%20Callaway's%20book%20list%2C%20with%20the%20Dylan%20book%20leading%20the%20fall%202023%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCallaway's%20publications%20are%20beautiful%2C%20whether%20created%20for%20children%2C%20art%20enthusiasts%2C%20or%20pop%20culture%20fans%2C%26quot%3B%20Todd%20McGarity%2C%20a%20then-vice%20president%20at%20Hachette%20Book%20Group%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hachettebookgroup.com%2Fhachette-book-group-news%2Fannouncing-new-distribution-agreement-between-hachette-book-group-and-callaway%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20press%20release%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20press%20release%20touted%20Callaway%20books%20as%20%26quot%3Bmust-have%20treasures%20that%20are%20made%20to%20hold%2C%20give%2C%20and%20receive%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20highly%20collectible%2C%20and%20very%20often%20appreciate%20significantly%20in%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221954%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Publisher%20Nicholas%20Callaway%20and%20Madonna.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2e18de98a37a4841f32ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221466%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPublisher%20Nicholas%20Callaway%20and%20Madonna.%3Cp%3EFrank%20Micelotta%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECallaway%20was%20founded%20more%20than%2040%20years%20ago%20by%20its%20CEO%2C%20Nicholas%20Callaway%2C%20described%20on%20the%20company's%20website%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Binternationally%20renowned%20publisher%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bwriter%2C%20photographer%20and%20teacher.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20company%2C%20founded%20as%20Callaway%20Editions%2C%20has%20published%20several%20high-profile%20projects%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmadonna-most-famous-looks-ranked-from-least-to-most-iconic-2022-6%23madonna-wore-a-revealing-version-of-a-traditional-german-dirndl-dress-to-the-1992-launch-for-her-book-sex-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMadonna's%201992%20book%20%26quot%3BSex%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20her%20children's%20book%20series%2C%20and%20the%202021%20book%20%26quot%3BThe%20Beatles%3A%20Get%20Back%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20account%20of%20%3Cs%3Et%3C%2Fs%3Ehe%20band's%20last%20studio%20album%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20It%20Be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20company%20also%20published%20a%20limited%20edition%20trilogy%20on%20the%20Sistine%20Chapel%2C%20which%20retails%20on%20its%20website%20for%20%2425%2C000.%20The%20company%20described%20the%20series%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpioneering%20technological%20breakthrough%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20press%20release%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20create%20the%20book%2C%20a%20team%20of%20photographers%20captured%20more%20than%20270%2C000%20digital%20images%20over%2067%20consecutive%20nights%20while%20the%20Sistine%20Chapel%20was%20closed%20to%20the%20public%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2024x17%20inch%2C%20822-page%2C%20three-volume%20set%20was%20the%20result%20of%20a%20five-year%20collaboration%20between%20Callaway%2C%20the%20Vatican%20Museums%2C%20and%20the%20Italian%20art%20publisher%20Scripta%20Maneant%2C%20the%20press%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%201%2C999%20copies%20were%20printed%2C%20of%20which%20only%20600%20were%20in%20English.%20%26quot%3BThe%20work%20will%20never%20be%20reprinted%2C%26quot%3B%20Callaway%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECallaway%2C%20in%20its%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy%20filing%2C%20said%20that%20it%20has%20between%201%20and%2049%20creditors%20and%20estimated%20both%20its%20assets%20and%20liabilities%20to%20be%20between%20%241%20million%20and%20%2410%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20coffee%20table-style%20printed%20books%20and%20e-books%2C%20Callway%20specializes%20in%20%26quot%3Bcomputer-animated%20television%20series%2C%20mobile%20and%20tablet%20applications%2C%20and%20trend-forward%2C%20design-driven%20lifestyle%20brands%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAcross%2040%20years%2C%20Callaway%20has%20created%20and%20published%20some%20of%20the%20most%20distinguished%20and%20successful%20illustrated%20books%20of%20our%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20website%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20collaborated%20both%20with%20world-renowned%20figures%20-%20presidents%2C%20popes%2C%20princesses%2C%20photographers%20and%20pop%20stars%20-%20and%20we%20have%20discovered%20and%20nurtured%20emerging%20artists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F25k-book-trilogy-publisher-bankruptcy-bob-dylan-callaway-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774516501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2ddb558b5806618e7debc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F25k-book-trilogy-publisher-bankruptcy-bob-dylan-callaway-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Callaway%20Arts%20%26amp%3B%20Entertainment%20filed%20for%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy.%20It%20owes%20unsecured%20creditors%20more%20than%20%244%20million%2C%20including%20%24450%2C000%20to%20Bob%20Dylan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nmusumeci%40businessinsider.com%20(Natalie%20Musumeci)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F25k-book-trilogy-publisher-bankruptcy-bob-dylan-callaway-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mardaani%203%20OTT%3A%20Watch%20Rani%20Mukerji's%20cop%20action%20thriller%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774516427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129820061%2Cimgsize-33868.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmardaani-3-ott-watch-rani-mukerjis-cop-action-thriller-date-and-platform-revealed%2Farticleshow%2F129820061.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129820061.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERani%20Mukerji%20returns%20as%20Shivani%20Roy%20in%20Mardaani%203%2C%20directed%20by%20Abhiraj%20Minawala.%20Streaming%20on%20Netflix%20from%20March%2027%20after%20%E2%82%B976.20cr%20worldwide%20run.%20Mixed%20reviews%3B%20fans%20love%20it%2C%20critics%20call%20it%20repetitive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmardaani-3-ott-watch-rani-mukerjis-cop-action-thriller-date-and-platform-revealed%2Farticleshow%2F129820061.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20husband%20and%20son%20went%20on%20a%20trip%20abroad.%20I'm%20glad%20I%20didn't%20go.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20son%20and%20husband%20at%20a%20match%20at%20Tottenham%20Stadium.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4062f5b58f1f0f93370f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20her%20husband%20and%20son%20went%20on%20a%20one-on-one%20trip%20while%20she%20stayed%20home.%20Seeing%20their%20smiles%20from%20inside%20Tottenham%20Stadium%20brought%20her%20joy.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ariel%20Frager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20husband%20and%20son%20took%20a%20trip%20abroad%20to%20attend%20a%20soccer%20match%20and%20eat%20pub%20food.%20I%20stayed%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20loved%20hearing%20about%20their%20adventures%20and%20was%20happy%20they%20got%20to%20spend%20this%20special%20time%20together.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20family%20trip%20I%20didn't%20go%20on%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20one%20of%20my%20favorites.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20soccer%20pitch%2C%20bright%20and%20not%20exactly%20natural%20green%2C%20was%20close%20enough%20to%20almost%20reach%20out%20and%20touch%20it.%20The%20November%20sunlight%20gleamed%2C%20illuminating%20the%20sweat%20dripping%20off%20the%20players.%20In%20the%20first%20quarter%2C%20Manchester%20United%20headed%20in%20a%20goal%2C%20and%20the%20visiting%20side%20cheered.%20The%20thrill%20of%20sitting%20field-side%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fpremier-league%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPremier%20League%20match%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20a%20dream%20come%20true%20for%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteen-after-school-job-youth-soccer-referee-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoccer-obsessed%20son%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20that%20I%20heard%20all%20about%20it%20from%20the%20comfort%20of%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMom!%20I%20can't%20believe%20it.%20Our%20seats%20were%20so%20awesome!%26quot%3B%20my%20son%20said%2C%20his%2013-year-old%20puberty-cracking%20voice%20rising%20unexpectedly%20into%20a%20fever%20pitch.%20%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20Manchester%20United%20score%20right%20in%20front%20of%20us!%26quot%3B%20Selfies%20from%20inside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnfl-tottenham-stadium-deal-london-nfl-team-2015-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETottenham%20Stadium%3C%2Fa%3E%20shared%20the%20glee%20of%20my%20husband%20and%20son's%20trip%20to%20London.%20I%20reveled%20in%20their%20joy%2C%20sympathetically%20joining%20in%2C%20even%20as%20I%20embraced%20the%20quiet%20solitude%20of%20a%20week%20home%20%E2%80%94%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I%20am%20the%20travel%20writer%20in%20our%20family%2C%20I%20had%20never%20been%20more%20excited%20about%20a%20trip%20that%20I%20wasn't%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a394bd2e-38ae-4e7c-b831-c11966fa3983%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20encouraged%20this%20one-on-one%20trip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20our%20son's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-citys-expensive-bar-mitzvahs-2014-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBar%20Mitzvah%20celebration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20husband%20took%20him%20to%20England.%20The%20dad-son-only%20trip%20focused%20on%20the%20things%20they%20love%3A%20soccer%2C%20pub%20food%2C%20and%20more%20soccer.%20Not%20only%20did%20I%20cheer%20for%20their%20adventures%2C%20but%20I%20also%20encouraged%20them%2C%20leaning%20on%20the%20knowledge%20that%20there%20are%20many%20positive%20cognitive%20and%20emotional%20benefits%20for%20kids%20when%20parents%20spend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveling-with-kids-solo-parent-vacation-planning-tips-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eone-on-one%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20their%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20son%20is%20shown%20outside%20of%20Tottenham%20Stadium.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4070c58b5806618e7e483%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20that%20a%20soccer-themed%20trip%20to%20London%20was%20a%20great%20way%20for%20her%20husband%20and%20son%20to%20share%20some%20one-on-one%20time.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ariel%20Frager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20spent%20about%20six%20months%20dreaming%20of%20this%20trip%20to%20England.%20My%20husband's%20father%20is%20from%20Manchester%2C%20making%20London%20an%20obvious%20choice%20for%20a%20short%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-sporting-events-across-the-globe-according-to-frequent-traveler-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoccer-based%20getaway%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Increasingly%20popular%2C%20sports%20holidays%20are%20taking%20root%20internationally%2C%20and%20soccer%20(sorry%2C%20football)%20is%20the%20primary%20driver%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnfl-london-games-the-novelty-of-american-football-in-england-has-worn-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esports-based%20holidays%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22950c6924-2b01-4777-a456-6e6857f6d8a3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20enjoyed%20some%20alone%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20serene%20quiet%20of%20our%20home%20was%20a%20welcome%20relief%20from%20the%20constant%20busyness%20of%20family%20life.%20I%20slept%20starfish-style%2C%20spread%20across%20our%20entire%20bed.%20Our%20house%20was%20tidy%2C%20the%20surfaces%20that%20I%20had%20cleaned%20days%20before%20stayed%20clear.%20I%20joked%20about%20eating%20cereal%20for%20dinner%20every%20night%2C%20delighting%20in%20not%20needing%20to%20cook%20for%20anyone%20but%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20phone%20pinged%20several%20times%20a%20day%20with%20the%20latest%20updates%20on%20the%20father-son%20adventures%2C%20and%20I%20was%20happy%20to%20learn%20what%20they%20were%20up%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20son%20poses%20near%20the%20Tower%20Bridge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4079ce98a37a4841f3857%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThough%20she%20wasn't%20with%20them%2C%20the%20author%20said%20she%20enjoyed%20it%20when%20her%20family%20sent%20pictures%20of%20their%20adventures%20abroad.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ariel%20Frager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFull%20English%20breakfasts%20started%20their%20days%20while%20I%20was%20happily%20tucked%20in%20bed%2C%20the%20eight-hour%20time%20difference%20stretching%20our%20ability%20to%20speak%20in%20real%20time.%20The%20texts%20and%20photos%20arrived%20in%20torrents%20when%20I%20turned%20on%20my%20phone%20each%20morning.%20While%20I%20drank%20my%20coffee%2C%20I%20lingered%20over%20shots%20of%20my%20guys%20posing%20in%20front%20of%20all%20the%20London%20landmarks.%20I%20was%20exactly%20where%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%2C%20and%20my%20son%20and%20husband%20were%20too%2C%20albeit%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20pond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e376b021-266d-4772-be7d-e7e362b612ae%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20three%20of%20us%20were%20all%20smiles%20about%20the%20trip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20often%20say%20that%20my%20favorite%20emotion%20is%20sympathetic%20joy%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20the%20feeling%20of%20happiness%20for%20someone%20else's%20happiness.%20There%20is%20a%20purity%20to%20sympathetic%20joy%3B%20to%20delight%20in%20other%20people's%20well-being%20feels%20like%20a%20boundless%20gift%20and%20the%20antidote%20to%20jealousy%20and%20envy.%20Being%20a%20mom%20has%20deepened%20my%20capacity%20to%20regard%20my%20son's%20(and%20my%20husband's)%20good%20fortune%20as%20my%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20their%20time%20in%20London%2C%20I%20was%20just%20so%20happy%20that%20my%20son%20and%20husband%20were%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-takes-summer-trip-without-alone-time-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ean%20adventure%20together%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20happy%20that%20they%20got%20to%20do%20all%20the%20things%20they%20love%2C%20and%20so%20very%20happy%20not%20to%20be%20dragged%20all%20over%20London%20looking%20for%20vintage%20soccer%20jerseys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20returned%20home%20with%20a%20suitcase%20full%20of%20soccer-filled%2C%20vibrant%20memories%20of%20the%20matches%20they%20saw%2C%20the%20memorable%20meals%2C%20and%20multiple%20gifts%20for%20me.%20But%20the%20best%20gift%20from%20their%20trip%20was%20knowing%20that%20sometimes%20staying%20home%20can%20offer%20something%20that%20traveling%20together%20can't%3A%20the%20opportunity%20to%20feel%20the%20joy%20that%20experience%20brings%20to%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20this%20is%20the%20true%20essence%20of%20motherhood%2C%20embracing%20pride%20and%20good%20wishes%20for%20our%20kids%20as%20they%20go%20forth%20to%20explore%20the%20world.%20Sometimes%20with%20us%2C%20and%20sometimes%20without.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffather-son-trip-london-soccer-abroad-international-travel-without-mom-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774516141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4062f5b58f1f0f93370f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffather-son-trip-london-soccer-abroad-international-travel-without-mom-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20husband%20took%20our%20soccer-obsessed%20son%20on%20an%20international%20trip%20to%20see%20a%20match.%20I%20didn't%20go%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20family%20trips.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ariel%20Frager)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffather-son-trip-london-soccer-abroad-international-travel-without-mom-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20US%20military%20is%20pushing%20up%20production%20for%20the%20weapons%20that%20could%20matter%20most%20in%20a%20major%20war%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20missile%20is%20fired%20from%20a%20launcher%20in%20a%20desert.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a5f8f2d3e2f1aef369d6a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223155%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETK%3Cp%3EUS%20Central%20Command%20Public%20Affairs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Defense%20is%20signing%20new%20deals%20with%20defense%20companies%20to%20boost%20production%20of%20critical%20weapons.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKey%20missiles%20and%20interceptors%20have%20seen%20extensive%20use%20in%20recent%20conflicts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOfficials%20and%20experts%20have%20raised%20concerns%20over%20insufficient%20stockpiles%20and%20production%20times.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Defense%20is%20pushing%20major%20defense%20companies%20to%20ramp%20up%20production%20of%20some%20of%20the%20most%20critical%20weapons%20in%20the%20US%20arsenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20deals%20between%20the%20Pentagon%20and%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20arms%20makers%20aimed%20at%20substantially%20increasing%20production%20of%20missiles%20and%20interceptors%20speak%20to%20both%20the%20expected%20demand%20for%20these%20weapons%20and%20concerns%20about%20existing%20stockpiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military%20has%20relied%20heavily%20on%20weapons%20like%20Patriot%20interceptors%2C%20SM-series%20missiles%2C%20THAAD%20interceptors%2C%20and%20more%20in%20recent%20conflicts%2C%20including%20the%20US-Israeli%20war%20with%20Iran.%20Many%20of%20these%20are%20also%20systems%20that%20US%20military%20planners%20deem%20critical%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-burns-through-key-missiles-needed-for-china-fight-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epotential%20showdown%20with%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227037f2e6-98ae-4263-bce1-d7dcfbd0e202%5C%22%3ETHAAD%20missile%20defense%20system%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224828%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c41526732a0245147130fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Etk%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Pfc%2C%20Josefina%20Garcia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Defense%20Department%20announced%20an%20agreement%20with%20Lockheed%20Martin%20and%20BAE%20Systems%20to%20quadruple%20the%20production%20of%20seekers%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-fired-500-million-top-missiles-defending-israel-from-attacks-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETerminal%20High%20Altitude%20Area%20Defense%3C%2Fa%3E%20interceptors.%20THAAD%20is%20designed%20to%20intercept%20short-%2C%20medium-%2C%20and%20intermediate-range%20ballistic%20missiles%20during%20the%20final%20phase%20of%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20advanced%20ground-based%20air%20defense%20assets%20operated%20by%20the%20US%2C%20THAAD%20can%20engage%20targets%20at%20ranges%20of%2093%20to%20124%20miles%20both%20inside%20and%20outside%20the%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewly-deployed-thaad-air-defense-system-gets-workout-middile-east-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETHAAD%20interceptors%3C%2Fa%3E%20strike%20the%20incoming%20missile%20directly%20rather%20than%20exploding%20nearby.%20The%20seekers%2C%20crucial%20missile%20components%20made%20by%20BAE%20Systems%2C%20are%20infrared%20sensors%20that%20enable%20interceptors%20to%20identify%20and%20lock%20onto%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20system's%20interceptors%20themselves%20are%20also%20getting%20a%20production%20boost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Lockheed%20Martin%20said%20that%20it%20planned%20to%20quadruple%20interceptor%20production%20from%2096%20a%20year%20to%20upward%20of%20400%20a%20year%20over%20the%20next%20seven%20years.%20Each%20interceptor%20costs%20about%20%2412.7%20million%20according%20to%20Missile%20Defense%20Agency%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETHAAD%20saw%20its%20first%20combat%20engagement%20in%202022%20against%20a%20ballistic%20missile%20launched%20by%20the%20Iran-backed%20Houthis%20in%20Yemen.%20Then%20in%20June%202025%2C%20the%20system%20intercepted%20Iranian%20missiles%20launched%20at%20Israel%2C%20with%20the%20US%20expending%20somewhere%20between%20100%20and%20150%20interceptors%20during%20the%2012-day%20fight.%20The%20US%20also%20relocated%20THAAD%20batteries%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20for%20its%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-gambles-drones-missiles-can-outlast-us-and-israel-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewar%20against%20Iran%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22569d32e8-277f-4157-a6e5-cfba54764a6b%5C%22%3ESM-6%20interceptors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c41546299090a8c09b62aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Etk%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Raytheon%2C%20a%20unit%20of%20RTX%20Corporation%2C%20said%20it%20would%20boost%20production%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-aircraft-spotted-sm6-missile-newly-tested-in-combat-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESM-6%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20over%20500%20annually%2C%20roughly%20a%20300%25%20increase%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20rate%20of%20125%20a%20year%2C%20in%20light%20of%20growing%20demand%20for%20the%20system.%20The%20company%20has%20made%20big%20investments%20in%20new%20production%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20SM-6%2C%20an%20interceptor%20in%20the%20Standard%20Missile%20series%2C%20which%20also%20includes%20the%20workhorse%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-destroyers-firing-top-interceptors-down-iranian-missiles-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESM-2%20and%20SM-3%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20costs%20about%20%244%20million.%20They're%20most%20suited%20for%20defense%20against%20aircraft%20and%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20as%20well%20as%20terminal%20defense%20against%20ballistic%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Navy%20has%20fired%20hundreds%20of%20SM%20interceptors%20in%20recent%20conflicts%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20since%20October%202023.%20Officials%20have%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuge-air-battles-show-us-needs-most-missile-war-china-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigh%20expenditure%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20draining%20stockpiles%2C%20prompting%20DoD%20to%20pursue%20expanded%20production%20capacity%20so%20that%20the%20US%20has%20more%20of%20its%20best%20interceptors%20for%20high-end%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaytheon%20is%20also%20increasing%20production%20of%20SM-3%20Block%20IB%20interceptors%20and%20SM-3%20Block%20IIA%20interceptors.%20Many%20of%20these%20munitions%2C%20the%20company%20said%2C%20will%20see%20double%20or%20quadruple%20their%20existing%20production%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c3ca84fa-c3d8-4c7e-bd44-cac0f3a97dd9%5C%22%3ETomahawk%20missiles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225339%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20Navy%20destroyer%20launches%20a%20Tomahawk%20missile%20as%20part%20of%20Operation%20Epic%20Fury.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bc458075bee4e0ee55e266%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223559%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20US%20Navy%2C%20if%20it%20were%20to%20take%20on%20an%20escort%20mission%20for%20tankers%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20might%20need%20to%20lean%20heavily%20on%20destroyers%20like%20the%20one%20seen%20here%20launching%20a%20Tomahawk%20missile.%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Navy%20photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERaytheon%20will%20also%20bump%20production%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-burned-through-more-tomahawks-iran-may-need-for-china-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETomahawk%20Land%20Attack%20Missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Maritime%20Strike%20variant%20to%20more%20than%201%2C000%20per%20year.%20Tomahawks%20are%20cruise%20missiles%20with%20long-range%20and%20precision%20targeting%2C%20making%20them%20a%20weapon-of-choice%20in%20recent%20US%20operations%