0period%20a%20year%20earlier%2C%20mainly%20due%20to%20smaller%20net%20international%20migration.%20The%20agency%20said%20the%20population%20of%20metro%20areas%20increased%200.6%25%20on%20average%20after%20a%201.1%25%20increase%20in%20the%20same%20period%20a%20year%20prior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20metro%20areas%20of%20Ocala%2C%20Florida%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmyrtle-beach-hotels-experiences-restaurants-travel-guide%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMyrtle%20Beach%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20the%20fastest%20population%20increases%20from%20July%201%2C%202024%2C%20to%20July%201%2C%202025%2C%20driven%20by%20positive%20net%20domestic%20migration%2C%20or%20more%20people%20coming%20in%20from%20somewhere%20within%20the%20US%20than%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FuHQkN%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Fastest-growing%20metros%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221003%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty-one%20of%20Florida's%2022%20metros%20grew%2C%20and%20most%20increased%20at%20a%20smaller%20pace%20than%20in%20the%20same%20period%20a%20year%20prior.%20The%20Miami%20metro%20area%20lost%200.1%25%20of%20its%20population%20due%20to%20negative%20net%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-florida-moved-north-carolina-expensive-traffic-weather-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edomestic%20migration%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cooler%20positive%20net%20international%20migration.%20Still%2C%20that%20wasn't%20the%20largest%20percent%20drop%20in%20population%20among%20US%20metros.%20Watertown%2C%20New%20York%2C%20took%20that%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%2