y%20remind%20you%20why%20your%20grandmother%20always%20did%20the%20same.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FA-farmer-shows-fresh-marigold-flowers-of-his-fields-in-Gajoth-Village-of-District-Doda-Jammu-and-Kashmir.-1.jpg%201400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FA-farmer-shows-fresh-marigold-flowers-of-his-fields-in-Gajoth-Village-of-District-Doda-Jammu-and-Kashmir.-1-300x197.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FA-farmer-shows-fresh-marigold-flowers-of-his-fields-in-Gajoth-Village-of-District-Doda-Jammu-and-Kashmir.-1-500x328.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FA-farmer-shows-fresh-marigold-flowers-of-his-fields-in-Gajoth-Village-of-District-Doda-Jammu-and-Kashmir.-1-768x503.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-264692%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22917%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhen%20October%20comes%2C%20pressing%20a%20few%20marigold%20seeds%20into%20the%20soil%20may%20remind%20you%20why%20your%20grandmother%20always%20did%20the%20same.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChoose%20the%20right%20spot%3A%20Pick%20a%20sunny%20place%20as%20marigolds%20thrive%20in%20full%20sunlight.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESoil%20prep%3A%20Use%20well-drained%2C%20moderately%20fertile%20soil%3B%20they%20are%20not%20too%20fussy.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESowing%20seeds%3A%20Sow%20seeds%20directly%20into%20the%20soil%20or%20start%20them%20in%20pots%3B%20cover%20lightly%20with%20soil.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWatering%3A%20Water%20regularly%20but%20avoid%20waterlogging%3B%20let%20the%20soil%20dry%20a%20little%20between%20watering.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECare%3A%20Remove%20dried%20flowers%20to%20encourage%20more%20blooms%20and%20keep%20t